          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The relative  photofission  cross  sections  for 234U",
                " were  measured  in the bremsstrahlung beam  of   SRC",
                " IPPE  microtron  in  the  g-ray energy region of 4.7",
                " - 9.0 MeV with step of 25 keV in  subbarrier  range.",
                " Energy   dependencies   of  the  photofission  cross",
                " section components for  234U  through  the  channels",
                " with the quantum numbers J-PI k = 1- 0 and 1- 1 were",
                " calculated using the results of the present work and",
                " previously measured angular distributions of fission",
                " fragments.  On  the  basis   of   these   data   the",
                " theoretical   analysis   of   the   234U  subbarrier",
                " photofission was carried out in the framework of the",
                " one-dimensional  double-humped  barrier model taking",
                " into account damping effects of  vibrational  states",
                " in the secondary minimum. Fission barrier parameters",
                " were adjusted.  The results of the present  research",
                " were  compared  with  the  data  obtained  on  other",
                " measurements."
              ]
            }
          ],
